# Gripper Grasp Service
# Close gripper to grasp an object

# Movement speed (0.0-1.0, 0 = use default)
float64 speed

# Gripper force (0.0-1.0, 0 = use default)
float64 force

# Whether to block until command completes
bool blocking
---
bool success
string message
bool is_grasped  # True if object is detected between fingers

